2. Open Arduino IED and write:
#define Apin A0 // A0 for ESP8266
void setup() {
 Serial.begin(9600);
}
void loop() {
 int sensorValue = analogRead(A0);
 Serial.println(sensorValue);
 
// Serial.println(ph);
delay(800);
}

2. Upload and open serial monitor " Ctrl + Shift + m"
3. Put node in 2 known Ph solution and calibrate with the values
eksample : https://www.mathsisfun.com/algebra/line-equation-2points.html where max value is 1023 and min is 0
